<h2 id="linear-transformations-in-3d" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#linear-transformations-in-3d"><span>Linear Transformations in 3D</span></a></h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p>3D에서의 선형 변환은 다음 행렬 곱셈으로 표현됨:</p>
<ul>
<li>3x3 matrix (in Cartesian coordinates)<br>
또는</li>
